                <h3 class="text-[18px] font-semibold self-center">Improve Public Services</h3>
            </div>

            <p class="description text-[15px] text-slate-800 font-light">
            We are working across Government to identify where targeted applications of AI can make the most radical improvements to existing services and the lives of people who use them.
        </p>
            <p class="description text-[15px] text-slate-800 font-light">
            Building and expanding on the work of the No10 Data Science team, i.AI will be empowered to use its central position to work across the public sector. Bringing world class skills and expertise to bear on areas of government that would not otherwise have the means to seize the opportunity presented by advancements in AI.
        </p>
            <p class="description text-[15px] text-slate-800 font-light">
            Our highly empowered engineers and developers will act as entrepreneurs in residence, proactively identifying opportunities to transform service provision.
        </p>
            <p class="description text-[15px] text-slate-800 font-light">
            We also know that those delivering services on the front line are often best placed to spot opportunities to improve them. Therefore, i.AI will make the most of the expertise and knowledge of our internal customers whilst putting the citizen at the centre of everything we deliver.
        </p>
