        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 w-[100%] md:w-[80%]">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-[18px] font-semibold self-center">Upskill Our People</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="description text-[15px] text-slate-800 font-light">
            Seizing the full potential of technology takes people. We are already upskilling thousands of Civil Servants with technical skills
            that will help them apply AI in their own areas of policy or operational delivery.
        </p>
            <p class="description text-[15px] text-slate-800 font-light">
            The Incubator for Artificial Intelligence will act as a central pool of truly world class AI experts with exceptional
            technical skills and a passion for improving the delivery of public services.
        </p>
            <p class="description text-[15px] text-slate-800 font-light">
            To that end, i.AI's expertise will help support the upskilling of thousands of existing Civil Servants in areas like programming,
            engineering, data science and machine learning. This training is already being delivered by initiatives
            such as the ONS Data Science Campus, One Big Thing and Evidence House.
        </p>
            <p class="description text-[15px] text-slate-800 font-light">
            All three of these initiatives will be supported by i.AI engineers and developers through the delivery of bootcamps,
            seminars and hackathons whereby a broad cross section of the Civil Service can access free technical training.
        </p>
            <p class="description text-[15px] text-slate-800 font-light">
            Modernising Government requires a higher floor and ceiling of technical skills. We will therefore focus on improving
            the general technical fluency of every Civil Servant regardless of grade and professions, whilst providing specialised
            training to existing experts and those in technical roles.
        </p>
